room_title: Escape room "Jailhouse Heist" by Escapologist in Lawton
room_description: Lost treasure? Every bandit's dream. A note has fallen into your hands regarding the late Sheriff's biggest secret. A train heist gone wrong. You and your rowdy gang of bandits have broken into the old Jailhouse to find the loot. The wall collapses leaving you and your gang inside. Unfortunately, the crooked Lawman had one last trick up his sleeve. Escape or face the ultimate sentence.
